data.description:
Discover this exceptional 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-story residence nestled within the highly coveted community you've been searching for! Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a pristine, modern design, thoughtfully curated interior finishes, and an inviting open floor plan. You'll find luxurious creamy ember cabinets adorned with speckled granite countertops and a taupe backsplash complemented by stylish tile flooring. The generously sized primary and secondary bedrooms provide added comfort and convenience. The garage features a glossy epoxy finish, adding a touch of sophistication to this already immaculate home.

This like-new home from Meritage boasts their renowned energy-efficient features, making it the perfect fusion of aesthetics and functionality.  Enjoy access to a variety of community amenities, including a well-appointed amenity center, a sparkling pool, a serene lake, excellent fishing opportunities, scenic jog-bike paths, and a charming park. Your dream home awaits!
